        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>很多时候我们会陷入对工具的惯性思维，即“手里拿着锤子，看什么任务都像钉子”。</p>\n<p>但其实还有另一个问题，我们手里拿着瑞士军刀，但还是想砸钉子。瑞士军刀能砸钉子吗？能。好用吗？不好用。去年有一门课程叫</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/24-3-24/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/24-3-24/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/24-3-24/index",
            "title": "2024-3-24",
            "date_modified": "2024-03-24T23:49:28.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-03-24T23:49:28.000Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "Elkeid",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>我没打算把每道题都拿出来讲. 只讲一些有意思的.</p>\n<p>下文的数学式中，$\\lnot$ 表示逻辑非，$&amp;$ 表示按位与，$\\mid$ 表示按位或，$\\bar{x}$ 表示 $x$ 按位取反，$\\opl</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/data-lab/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/data-lab/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/data-lab/index",
            "title": "Data Lab",
            "date_modified": "2024-03-08T23:12:57.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-03-08T23:12:57.000Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "Elkeid",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>Proxy Lab 要求我们自己写 Makefile，所以用 C++ 是完全可行的。</p>\n<h2>Part A</h2>\n<p>Part A 要求做一个并发的 HTTP 代理。比较先进的思路可以考虑 I/O 多路复用</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/proxy-lab/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/proxy-lab/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/proxy-lab/index",
            "title": "Proxy Lab 的并发设计",
            "date_modified": "2024-03-04T18:48:14.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-03-04T18:48:14.000Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "Elkeid",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>完整代码见 <a href=\"https://github.com/Elkeid-me/csapp-3e-malloc-lab\">Elkeid-me/csapp-3e-malloc-lab</a></p>\n<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>众所周</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/malloc-lab/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/malloc-lab/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
