        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>TeXmacs，特别是其国产 fork <a href=\"https://gitee.com/XmacsLabs/mogan\">墨干编辑器</a>，这两个东西我已经批判过一番了。但是呢，鉴于 TeXmacs / 墨干的信</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/comments-on-texmacs-and-mogan-editor/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/comments-on-texmacs-and-mogan-editor/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/comments-on-texmacs-and-mogan-editor/index",
            "title": "评 TeXmacs 与墨干编辑器",
