        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h2>Exercise 1 and 2</h2>\n<h3><code>mmio_map_region()</code></h3>\n<p>调用 <code>boot_map_region()</code> 即可。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-c\">void *mmio_map_region(ph</code></pre>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/os-lab-4/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/os-lab-4/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
