        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>本文章描述了在 Ubuntu 22.04 上配置 JOS Lab 环境的过程。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>安装必要的工具软件与库：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt install build-essential </code></pre>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/setup-jos-lab-environment/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://elkeid-me.github.io/posts/setup-jos-lab-environment/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
